    <p>You agree to use our services only for lawful purposes and in accordance with these Terms. You may not:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white mb-4">
      <li>Use our services to violate any applicable laws or regulations.</li>
      <li>Attempt to interfere with the functionality or security of our website or services.</li>
      <li>Use our content or services without permission for commercial purposes.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3>2. Intellectual Property</h3>
    <p>All content on our website, including text, images, and code, is owned by Thomas's Game Development Studio or its licensors and is protected by copyright and other intellectual property laws. You may not:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white mb-4">
      <li>Copy, reproduce, or distribute our content without prior written consent.</li>
      <li>Use our trademarks, logos, or designs without permission.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3>3. User Content</h3>
    <p>If you submit content to us (e.g., feedback, inquiries), you grant us a non-exclusive, royalty-free license to use, modify, and display that content for the purpose of providing our services. You are responsible for ensuring your content does not violate any laws or third-party rights.</p>
    
