    <p>We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your access to our services at our discretion, particularly if you violate these Terms. You may stop using our services at any time.</p>
    
    <h3>6. Governing Law</h3>
    <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of Retro City, RC. Any disputes arising from these Terms shall be resolved in the courts of Retro City.</p>
    
    <h3>7. Contact Us</h3>
    <p>If you have questions about these Terms, please contact us at:</p>
    <p>
      Email: <a href="mailto:support@thomasgames.studio" class="text-yellow-300 hover:underline">support@thomasgames.studio</a><br />
      Address: 123 Pixel Lane, Retro City, RC 12345
    </p>
    
